text: 脱肛：鸡的直肠部分脱出于肛门之外叫脱肛，在产蛋高峰期易发生脱肛。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"脱肛","labels":["disease"]},{"start":23,"end":28,"text":"输卵管内膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"产道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 脱肛的发生，多由于产蛋多，营养不足，体质较差，输卵管内膜分泌的起润滑作用的油脂不足，产道涩滞；或产蛋过大，强力努责；

label: [{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 或因停产，输卵管收缩，产后泄殖腔未完全恢复正常即受惊吓；

label: [{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"慢性炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肛门","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 输卵管或肛门的慢性炎症，由于炎症产物对局部的刺激，病鸡为了排出刺激物，常不断增加努责；

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"便秘","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"粪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":22,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":33,"text":"后躯风湿","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"不能站立","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"腹部下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":49,"text":"腹压加大","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"腹部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 便秘时，排粪过度努责；冬春季节舍内温度低，鸡运动不足，易患后躯风湿，不能站立，使腹部下垂，腹压加大；

label: [{"start":1,"end":3,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"啄癖","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"脱肛","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"脱肛","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 对鸡群管理不善或有啄癖等原因均可造成脱肛。脱肛与鸡的品种也有一定关系。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"脱肛","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"肛门","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":23,"text":"肛门流出一种黄白色黏稠液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"黄白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"黏稠液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":32,"text":"附在肛门周围的绒毛","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":32,"text":"肛门周围的绒毛","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 发生脱肛的初期，可见从肛门流出一种黄白色黏稠液附在肛门周围的绒毛上。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"肛门","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"直肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":18,"text":"肉红色物质","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"糜烂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"溃疡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":58,"end":59,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":63,"end":64,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 然后从肛门脱出约2厘米长的肉红色物质，即直肠脱出的部分，此脱出部分若不及时护理则可发生炎症、糜烂或溃疡，并可招致其他鸡啄伤而致鸡死亡。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":24,"text":"各种营养成分配比合理","labels":["control"]}]
text: 1.加强饲养管理：饲养过程中各种营养成分配比合理，增强体质。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"及时发现病鸡","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"隔离饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":26,"end":34,"text":"高锰酸钾温水溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":37,"end":43,"text":"硼酸温水溶液","labels":["drug"]},{"start":37,"end":45,"text":"硼酸温水溶液洗净","labels":["control"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"复位","labels":["control"]}]
text: 及时发现病鸡，并隔离饲养，防止啄伤脱出部分用0.1%高锰酸钾温水溶液或2%硼酸温水溶液洗净、复位，早、午、晚每天处理3次，连续处理几天，可不再脱出。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"炎症","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"恶臭味","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"洗净","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":20,"end":25,"text":"涂以土霉素","labels":["control"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"土霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"金霉素软膏","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 如有炎症发生，并有恶臭味时，洗净、消毒后涂以土霉素或金霉素软膏；

label: [{"start":2,"end":9,"text":"坏死的黏膜组织","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"碘酊","labels":["drug"]},{"start":25,"end":28,"text":"紫药水","labels":["drug"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"消炎粉","labels":["drug"]},{"start":43,"end":48,"text":"作烟包缝合","labels":["control"]},{"start":10,"end":16,"text":"洗净后应刮去","labels":["control"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"黏膜组织","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 如有坏死的黏膜组织，洗净后应刮去，轻症的涂以碘酊或紫药水，并撒外用消炎粉；重症者可考虑作烟包缝合。
